<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thanks for making your reservation of <%= @panels %>, <%= @name %></h1>
    <p>
      We'll get back to you as soon as we can about your reservation.<br/>
      In the meantime, check back at <%= @url %> for news. <br />
    </p>
    <p>Cheers,</p>
    <p>The 98Lumens team</p>

    <p>=======================</p>
    <p>Reservation summary <br />
      ========================
      <br />
      Name: <%= @name %> <br />
      Email: <%= @email %> <br />
      Phone: <%= @phone %> <br />
      Panels reserved: <%= @panels %> <br />
      Message: <%= @message %>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>